The Keiser Report  No. 192
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Tuesday, 04 October 2011


[sebaygo1]


This time Max and Stacy talk about bailouts, defaults and currency wars in Europe as one analyst suggests the return of the Deutschmark is imminent. 

In the second half of the show, Max Keiser interviews Steve Woolfe, City of London spokesman for the UK Independence Party, about his party's suggestion that Greece return to the drachma and regain the ability to address its own economic problems.
